<a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/I-fokus-paa-produktsikkerhed/Sikkerhed-omkring-segboards" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-twitter-square twitter-brand"></i></a>
<a href="https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/I-fokus-paa-produktsikkerhed/Sikkerhed-omkring-segboards" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-pinterest-square pinterest-brand"></i></a>
<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/I-fokus-paa-produktsikkerhed/Sikkerhed-omkring-segboards" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-linkedin-square linkedin-brand"></i></a>
<a href="mailto:?subject=Sikkerhed omkring segboards &body=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/I-fokus-paa-produktsikkerhed/Sikkerhed-omkring-segboards" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-envelope-o mail-brand"></i></a>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl) -->
</div>
      <br>
      <hr>
        
              
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Sikkerhedskravene for de fleste segboards reguleres af Maskindirektivet, som Arbejdstilsynet er dansk myndighed for. Enkelte segboards markedsføres som legetøj og reguleres af Legetøjsdirektivet, der hører under Sikkerhedsstyrelsen.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Sikkerhedsstyrelsen har siden slutningen af november 2015 haft opmærksomheden rettet mod sikkerheden ved segboards, bl.a. på baggrund af en meddelelse fra de engelske myndigheder om segboards, der ikke levede op til sikkerhedskravene. Styrelsen og Arbejdstilsynet har iværksat en lang række initiativer. Blandt andet grænsekontrol, test af tilfældigt udvalgte boards og information til importører om sikkerhedskravene.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Sikkerhedskravene for de fleste segboards reguleres af Maskindirektivet, som Arbejdstilsynet er dansk myndighed for. Enkelte segboards markedsføres som legetøj og reguleres af Legetøjsdirektivet, der hører under Sikkerhedsstyrelsen.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Du kan læse mere om reglerne for markedsføring af segboards på 
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
<a href="http://arbejdstilsynet.dk/da/regler/bekendtgorelser/i/indretning-mv-af-maskiner/information-om-segboards.aspx" target="_blank">Arbejdstilsynets hjemmeside</a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Hvis Sikkerhedsstyrelsen finder anledning til indgreb mod konkrete produkter, vil importør eller forhandler blive bedt om at foretage det fornødne, eksempelvis at stoppe salget eller tilbagekalde produkter fra forbrugerne. Der vil blive informeret om evt. farlige produkter på Sikkerhedsstyrelsens hjemmeside Sik.dk.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Spørgsmål og svar om segboards</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Sikkerhedsstyrelsen har fået en række spørgsmål om segboards. Nedenfor kan svarene ses.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Er mit segboard farligt?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl) -->

<ul>

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Sikkerhedsstyrelsen har udarbejdet en generel vejledning om brug af segboards. Den kan ses på 
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
<a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../Forbruger/Produktsikkerhed/Brug-produkter-sikkert/Husk-sikkerheden-ved-koeb-og-brug-af-segboards.html" target="_blank">http://www.sik.dk/Forbruger/Produktsikkerhed/Brug-produkter-sikkert/Husk-sikkerheden-ved-koeb-og-brug-af-segboards</a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Det er importøren til EU, som er ansvarlig for, at et produkt er sikkert. Har du spørgsmål til et konkret segboard, skal du henvende dig, hvor du har købt segboardet.</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

</ul>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Skal segboardet være mærket med modelbetegnelse og fabrikantens navn?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Ja, det er et krav, at et segboard er forsynet med &nbsp;et type-, parti-, serie- eller modelnummer eller en anden form for angivelse, der kan identificere det, på selve brættet.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Ligeledes skal fabrikantens navn, registrerede firmanavn eller registrerede varemærke og kontaktadresse fremgå af selve brættet.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Skal der medfølge en dansk brugsanvisning&nbsp;</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>til et segboard</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Ja, det er et krav, at der medfølger en brugsanvisning &nbsp;med sikkerhedsinformation på dansk.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Skal der medfølge en overensstemmelseserklæring?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>EU-overensstemmelseserklæringen er en erklæring, hvor fabrikanten oplyser, hvilke EU-direktiver segboardet er fremstillet i overensstemmelse med.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Krav om medlevering af fabrikantens overensstemmelseserklæring afhænger af, hvilket regelsæt segboardet hører under.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Der er ikke krav om medlevering af overensstemmelseserklæring til forbrugerne, hvis et segboard er markedsført i overensstemmelse med legetøjsdirektivet.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Segboards, som er omfattet af maskindirektivet, skal leveres til forbrugerne med en brugsanvisning med en kopi af overensstemmelseserklæringen på dansk.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Kan jeg få pengene tilbage for et produkt, som ikke er CE-mærket?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl) -->

<ul>

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Du bør henvende dig hos forhandleren med spørgsmålet, om der er returret på dit produkt.</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Der er generel information om fortrydelsesret på 
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
<a href="http://www.forbrug.dk/" target="_blank">www.forbrug.dk</a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

</ul>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Hvad betyder CE-mærket?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl) -->

<ul>

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Et CE-mærke sættes på et produkt af fabrikanten, efter at der er udarbejdet en overensstemmelseserklæring, hvor fabrikanten erklærer, at produktet lever op til sikkerhedskravene i lovgivningen.</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>En producent må kun sætte et CE-mærke på sit produkt, hvis kravene er opfyldt.</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>CE-mærket skal placeres på selve produktet, ikke alene på emballagen.</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>På Sikkerhedsstyrelsens hjemmeside er der et overblik over, hvad CE-mærket betyder: 
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
<a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/Maerkning-af-produkter/Hvad-er-CE-Maerkning.html" target="_blank">http://www.sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/Maerkning-af-produkter/Hvad-er-CE-Maerkning</a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Produkter, der er omfattet af CE-mærkningsdirektiver, skal være CE-mærkede. Et produkt kan være omfattet af flere direktiver, og det er importørens ansvar at identificere, hvilke direktiver et konkret produkt er omfattet af, ligesom importøren skal kunne dokumentere, at produktet lever op til kravene.&nbsp;</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

</ul>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
      
      
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/page_list_subitems.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/page_list_subitems.tpl) -->
<!-- page_list_subitems -->    <div class="list-group">
    </div><!-- /page_list_subitems -->

